version_description: I always play this version and I think it sounds better and more original than the others.
Some chords are different than the other versions.

My version is different because mine is taken from Dave Grohl playing it without the rest of the band.  Other tabs put the third verse with the chords for the chorus which were also wrong.  All in all I watched Dave Grohl play it in a video and he makes it so much more simple than people are trying to make it.
My hero is an amazing song this version I put together from watching Dave Grohl play it live so I think it is accurate Enjoy playing. https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=nGa1syRUbRQ.
